---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — BKK Songkran" description="Privacy policy for BKK Songkran.com. How we collect, use, and protect your data." canonical="https://bkksongkran.com/privacy">

  <section class="pt-36 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3" style="color:#006479;">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="font-headline font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-2" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem);color:#003345;line-height:0.95;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm mb-12" style="color:#6b8fa3;">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:#326177;">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Who we are</h2>
          <p>BKK Songkran (<strong>bkksongkran.com</strong>) is an independent festival information guide for Songkran 2026 in Bangkok, Thailand. We are not affiliated with any festival organiser, ticketing platform, or government body.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">What data we collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We collect minimal data to operate the site:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
            <li><strong>Analytics data</strong> — page views, session duration, referral source, device/browser type, approximate country. Collected via Google Analytics through Google Tag Manager. This data is anonymised and aggregated.</li>
            <li><strong>AI chat messages</strong> — when you use the Nong AI guide, your messages are sent to OpenAI's API to generate responses. We do not store your chat history on our servers beyond the current session. OpenAI's data handling is governed by <a href="https://openai.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline" style="color:#006479;">OpenAI's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies and local storage</strong> — we use browser local storage to save your Survival Kit checklist progress locally on your device. This data never leaves your browser. See the cookie section below.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">How we use your data</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>To understand how visitors use the site and improve content</li>
            <li>To provide the AI guide feature (Nong)</li>
            <li>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing</li>
            <li>We do <strong>not</strong> build user profiles or serve targeted advertising</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div id="cookies">
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We use the following cookies and storage mechanisms:</p>
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border" style="border-color:rgba(192,232,255,0.6);">
            <table class="w-full text-xs">
              <thead style="background:rgba(225,243,255,0.7);">
                <tr>
                  <th class="text-left px-4 py-3 font-bold" style="color:#003345;">Cookie / Storage</th>
                  <th class="text-left px-4 py-3 font-bold" style="color:#003345;">Purpose</th>
                  <th class="text-left px-4 py-3 font-bold" style="color:#003345;">Type</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody style="color:#326177;">
                <tr class="border-t" style="border-color:rgba(192,232,255,0.4);">
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono">_ga, _ga_*</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Google Analytics — anonymous usage statistics</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Analytics (2 years)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t" style="border-color:rgba(192,232,255,0.4);">
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono">check-*</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Survival Kit checklist state (localStorage, your device only)</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Functional</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t" style="border-color:rgba(192,232,255,0.4);">
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono">GTM cookies</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Google Tag Manager container</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Analytics</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3">You can manage cookie preferences using the CookieYes widget (bottom-left of the page) or your browser settings. Declining analytics cookies does not affect your ability to use the site.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Third-party services</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
            <li><strong>Google Analytics / GTM</strong> — usage analytics. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline" style="color:#006479;">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>OpenAI</strong> — powers the Nong AI guide. Messages are processed via their API. <a href="https://openai.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline" style="color:#006479;">OpenAI Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — fonts loaded from Google servers. Google may collect connection data. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline" style="color:#006479;">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Your rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete data we hold about you. Since we collect minimal identifying data, requests are typically straightforward. Contact us via the site for any privacy requests.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">For EU/EEA residents: you have rights under GDPR including access, rectification, erasure, and objection to processing. Our lawful basis for analytics is legitimate interest (improving the site). You may withdraw consent via the cookie settings at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Data retention</h2>
          <p>Google Analytics data is retained for 14 months. Local storage data (checklist) stays on your device until you clear your browser data. We do not retain AI chat messages server-side.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy as the site evolves. Material changes will be reflected in the "Last updated" date above. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of the current policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions or requests: use the feedback form on the site.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
